metadata.name: 𝗧𝘂𝗻𝗲𝗱 P𝗲𝗼𝗽𝗹𝗲
metadata.description:
It is very scary that you go on with your life without feeling.
Just like these people.
Tune yourself but right.
_____________________

My brother Mazdak and I did this illustration together. Mazdak has Down syndrome. We work together. I use Mazdak's paintings in my works. And I create a new composition. We are a team.
